content:
Been on the Gold Coast for half a day & I've never seen so many young girls with thigh tattoos in my life.

,#,Yuck,
Welcome to the Vegas of Australia! Only minus the casinos... and attractions... and money... and women... and shows.
I wouldn't say it's minus the women. Plenty up here for a young buck to have a look at.
it's the Daytona beach of Australia.
